name: Communication
notes: Communication regarding administrative or formal matters (missing parts, irregularities...)
creator: system

name: Created
notes: Creation date of matter - for attaching tasks necessary before anything else
creator: system

name: Deemed withrawn
notes: Decision needing a reply, such as further processing
creator: system

name: Examiner Action
notes: AKA Office Action, i.e. anything related to substantive examination
creator: system

name: Expiry
notes: Do not use nor change - present for internal functionality
creator: system

name: Pay
notes: Use for any fees to be paid
creator: system

name: Prepare
notes: Any further action to be done by the responsible (comments, pre-handling, ...)
creator: system

name: Priority Claim
notes: Use as link to the priority matter
creator: system

name: Produce
notes: Any further documents to be filed (inventor designation, priority document, missing parts...)
creator: system

name: Published
notes: For EP, this means publication WITH the search report (A1 publ.)
creator: system

name: Received
notes: Date the case was received from the client
creator: system

name: Refused
notes: This is the final decision, that can only be appealed - do not mistake with an exam report
creator: system
